{"tid":1145934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[深圳好好玩]肝癌個案中國冠絕全球　專家拆解地溝油是元兇","createTime":"2019-05-09T02:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T02:19:34.000Z","uid":49359,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"84eed61f25f4c3ea3f64f2d35cc3e13edeedd837","tid":1145934,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T02:36:20.000Z","msg":"內地食安問題亦一直為人詬病，其中黃曲霉素常見於花生及發霉食物，可形成肝癌細胞， 已被世衞劃定為一級致癌物，惟內地地溝油或劣質花生油不時被驗出黃曲霉素含量超標，故相信內地人日常飲食時，或不時攝取了該種毒素，以致容易誘發肝癌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2334625/%E8%82%9D%E7%99%8C%E6%96%B0%E7%97%87%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%86%A0%E7%B5%95%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E3%80%80%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%8B%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%9C%B0%E6%BA%9D%E6%B2%B9%E5%90%AB%E9%BB%83%E6%9B%B2%E9%9C%89%E7%B4%A0%E6%98%AF%E5%85%83%E5%85%87?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2334625%2F%25E8%2582%259D%25E7%2599%258C%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2597%2587%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%25B5%2595%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%258B%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%25BA%259D%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%2590%25AB%25E9%25BB%2583%25E6%259B%25B2%25E9%259C%2589%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%2585%2587%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyftTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=ad7bc96e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2334625/%E8%82%9D%E7%99%8C%E6%96%B0%E7%97%87%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%86%A0%E7%B5%95%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E3%80%80%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%8B%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%9C%B0%E6%BA%9D%E6%B2%B9%E5%90%AB%E9%BB%83%E6%9B%B2%E9%9C%89%E7%B4%A0%E6%98%AF%E5%85%83%E5%85%87?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"6dc577e21ae79152e557b8be983b1cf23e9b5779","tid":1145934,"uid":55913,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:06:25.000Z","msg":"黨既禮物"},{"pid":"88124b0929fb81c9120f5ecdcef34c859614defd","tid":1145934,"uid"